{"type":"message","id":"ab649c2a","parentId":"e86efd9f","timestamp":"2026-04-30T01:38:57.453Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_JsUBZKdo7q5CHbhoGO444IJe","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: ths-local-holdings\ndescription: \"Inspect Tonghuashun/同花顺真实持仓 from two sources: (1) the 10jqka 投资账本 web app (`tzzb.10jqka.com.cn`) when a reusable browser session or exported request is available, and (2) local macOS Tonghuashun app ledger files as a fail-closed fallback. Use when the user mentions 同花顺持仓、投资账本网页、10jqka tzzb 链接、同花顺 App、本地账本、多账户混仓、账本识别、真实持仓校准, or when reports/alerts are using the wrong holdings scope and you need a verified source instead of guessing.\"\n---\n\n# Ths Local Holdings\n\n优先把 **10jqka 投资账本网页** 当主源；只有网页 API / 登录态暂时拿不到时，才退回本机 `XcsLscjDataFile_*` 账本文件。\n核心原则不变：**宁可 fail closed，也不要猜主账号/猜主持仓。**\n\n## Workflow\n\n### 1. 先探测网页主源是否可用\n\n先运行：\n\n```bash\npython3 ~/.openclaw/skills/ths-local-holdings/scripts/ths_tzzb_web_probe.py scan \\\n  --page-url 'https://tzzb.10jqka.com.cn/pc/index.html#/myAccount/a/C6QIQGQ' \\\n  --out /tmp/tzzb_web_probe.json\n```\n\n这一步会给出三类证据：\n- 前端 bundle 里是否存在 `/caishen_fund/...` API 路由\n- 本机 Chromium/Edge/Chrome profile 里是否存在 `tzzb.10jqka.com.cn` 历史、cookie、localStorage 痕迹\n- 当前环境是否缺少 Playwright / Selenium / 可自动化能力\n\n### 2. 最短路径：HAR / cURL → request-json\n\n如果用户能提供 **HAR** 或 **Copy as cURL**，先转成 request-json，再接 replay。\n\n#### 2.1 HAR 转 request-json\n\n```bash\npython3 ~/.openclaw/skills/ths-local-holdings/scripts/ths_tzzb_web_probe.py convert-har \\\n  --har /path/to/tzzb.har \\\n  --url-contains stock_position \\\n  --out /tmp/tzzb_stock_position_request.json\n```\n\n说明：\n- 默认优先挑选 URL 命中 `/caishen_fund/...` 已知接口的条目\n- 若 HAR 里命中多个条目，可加 `--url-contains stock_position` 或 `--entry-index 12`\n- 输出文件就是 replay 可直接消费的 `request-json`\n\n#### 2.2 cURL 转 request-json\n\n把浏览器 Network 里的 **Copy as cURL (bash)** 原样存成文本文件后运行：\n\n```bash\npython3 ~/.openclaw/skills/ths-local-holdings/scripts/ths_tzzb